	<meta property="og:description" content="I‚Äôve been sitting here for the past twenty minutes, trying to figure out how to start this post. I hate it when this happens. I have nightmares about it, even. Well, let‚Äôs see. How about a photograph? Maybe it will jump-start something. One can hope. One can also, while hoping, tiptoe over to the fridge and steal some of the peppermint bark in that photograph, even though it‚Äôs supposed to be saved for holiday gifts. That‚Äôs another option. Just don‚Äôt tell Brandon, because I told him earlier today that he couldn‚Äôt have any. Then again, he‚Äôs over at the restaurant space right now, drinking a beer and eating Cool(!) Ranch(!) Doritos(!) while he rips out the carpet, so it‚Äôs really&hellip;" />
