    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Try sandwiching Nabisco chocolate wafers around mint-infused dark chocolate ganache, allow to firm-up in fridge, then slide the wheel around in some melted white chocolate until thoroughly coated. Sprinkle the tips with crushed candy cane, refridgerate again, and then wrap up in clear cello bags tied with festive ribbon. Makes an impressive gift.</p>
