    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh my&#8230;in all the excitement of exams, I have forgotten about Christmas baking! </></>The last time I made peppermint bark, the peppermint extract caused the chocolate to seize&#8230;I suppose that adding the extract before melting the chocolate would fix that? I hope so, because this looks fantastic (although no one had any problems inhaling the somewhat-bumpy bark from last year).</p>
