    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Those looked great!  I recently made my first attempt at peppermint bark this year (I wished I saw this recipe first).  But I tried making it the slacker-method and used left over chocolate graham crackers for the bottom layer.  It was still good, but I think I&#8217;ll need to try your recipe (I still have a bunch of candy canes to use up!).</p>
