    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just made these this morning using crushed candy canes and big blocks of Callebaut chocolate I chopped up. Now, I figure I made a batch and a half and with my chocolate costs the whole thing was about $18 to make. A) way cheaper than buying the bark at a good chocolate shop and B) so much better!</></>This one has earned a spot in my holiday baking for years to come. Thanks Molly!</p>
