      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-12117' data-commentid="12117" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-12117" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Little Welsh House" aria-label='Reply to Little Welsh House'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-12118" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">YolandaG</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/12/look-at-that/#comment-12118"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-12-09T18:31:10-05:00">Tuesday, December 9, 2014 at 6:31 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Love your stories with your recipes.  I am going to make this tomorrow night for a Holiday Bake-Off at my work.  I&#39;ll let you know if I win!  My flan came in 2nd last year!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-12118' data-commentid="12118" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-12118" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to YolandaG" aria-label='Reply to YolandaG'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-12119" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/02362400193461181447" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Kim</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/12/look-at-that/#comment-12119"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-12-22T21:13:37-05:00">Monday, December 22, 2014 at 9:13 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>It turned out delicious, but am I the only bonehead who thought you meant 30 candy canes instead of the little round wrapped peppermint candies like Brachs and now has a cutting board full of extra broken candy to use up somehow? Aaaah, I blame mommy brain. And living abroad, candy canes are about the only peppermint candy you can find here, &#038; even those aren&#39;t easy to come by.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-12119' data-commentid="12119" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-12119" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Kim" aria-label='Reply to Kim'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-12120" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/12/look-at-that/#comment-12120"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-12-24T06:09:48-05:00">Wednesday, December 24, 2014 at 6:09 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just finished making these &#8211; and, ummm, yeah, they&#39;re good, ha!  Used Lindt White Coconut (cause am in Hawaii) and red and white striped peppermint buttermints (cause that&#39;s all I could find) and wow, really delicious.  Thank you!  Happy Holidays! </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-12120' data-commentid="12120" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-12120" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anonymous" aria-label='Reply to Anonymous'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-12121" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/12/look-at-that/#comment-12121"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-12-24T06:13:26-05:00">Wednesday, December 24, 2014 at 6:13 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh, and used coconut cream from a can for the regular cream and it worked perfectly (fyi for all those sensitive to dairy overload out there!).  </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-12121' data-commentid="12121" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-12121" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anonymous" aria-label='Reply to Anonymous'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-12122" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Isa</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/12/look-at-that/#comment-12122"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-12-28T22:49:37-05:00">Sunday, December 28, 2014 at 10:49 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks for posting this recipe! It made my grand father really happy, he absolutely loved them. I had a few too =P</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-12122' data-commentid="12122" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-12122" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Isa" aria-label='Reply to Isa'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-44603" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Karin Tracy</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/12/look-at-that/#comment-44603"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2015-12-23T17:02:58-05:00">Wednesday, December 23, 2015 at 5:02 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just circling back to thank you again (I thanked you back in 2011 or so) and to note that I&#8217;ve made these every year since 2008, save one. That particular holiday season, I plain forgot to make them and I sure did pay for it with cranky nieces/nephews. Such a crowdpleaser, this bark is! Happy holidays to you and your family.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-44603' data-commentid="44603" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-44603" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Karin Tracy" aria-label='Reply to Karin Tracy'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-60311" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
