    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is the best peppermint bark ever! It&#8217;s been a Christmas staple for years. It wouldn&#8217;t be Christmas without it. Thank you for sharing. xo</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-60311' data-commentid="60311" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-60311" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Jaimie" aria-label='Reply to Jaimie'>Reply</a>    </div>
