    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly,<br />
This has been a Christmas staple of mine since you first posted it 10 years ago.  I can&#8217;t express how much I love this recipe.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-70811' data-commentid="70811" data-postid="1064" data-belowelement="comment-70811" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Kate" aria-label='Reply to Kate'>Reply</a>    </div>
