    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just bought the chocolate to make the 2020 batches.  Pandemic, wild fires, political chaos, economic struggles; closer to home, son with a TBI, then I was struck by a car (we&#8217;re both recovering).  We need this peppermint bark more than ever this year. Thank you, again, Molly. Happy holidays, may 2021 be a better year for everyone.</p>
